[{h1}civix: unix system library for Civstack]
Civix contains standard unix functions that exist in most language's "sys"
library such as [$sleep], [$epoch] etc. It also contains a powerful [$Sh{}]
type and convieience [$sh()] function for executing system shell commands,
either synchronously or asynchronously using the LAP protocol (see
[<lap.html>].

